... more Photo: Kevin Mazur/Getty Images Image 50 of 50 The Oscars' cutest couples stun at the 89th Academy Awards red carpet 1 / 50 Back to Gallery The thing some of us long for more than the gowns and the golden statues is the undeniable love and passion displayed at the Academy Awards.
On Sunday, Feb. 26, the 89th annual award show that honors Hollywood's best brought forth pairings of all kinds.
Some A-list celebrities appeared with their spouses and significant others. We are lucky enough to vicariously live through Chrissy Teigen and John Legend's adorable relationship on the biggest night in Hollywood. They can't stop being cute.
FASHION ARCHIVES: The dress worn by every best actress winner
The 2017 Oscar Academy Award Show is finally here and the stars are just starting to make their grand entrance onto the red carpet. Ruth Negga, Lucas Hedges and Auli’i Cravalho are just a few stars who have been seen walking the red carpet at the 89th Academy Awards along with “Loving” actress Ruth Negga. Other actors include “Hacksaw Ridge” actor Luke Bracey, “Manchester by the Sea” actor Lucas Hedges, and “Moana” actress Auli’i Cravalho.
Media: MediaOS Video Other big stars like Academy Award nominee Dev Patel and Lin-Manuel Miranda, walked the carpet with their moms. Those moments make for the sweetest photos and we can also see from where they get their good looks.
Jackie Chan shook up protocol and arrived with his....stuffed pandas. No judgment here.
And when you just want to soak up the fun and enjoy the occasion, why not bring your BFF? Thank Michelle Williams and Busy Phillips for showing us bestie goals.
Check out the gallery above for the cutest couples at the 89th Academy Awards and some throwback red carpet moments.
